data.description: SELLER MUST MOVE & IS HIGHLY MOTIVATED! PRICE REDUCTION AND SELLER CONCESSION OF $5000 Buyers Credit (to buy down interest rate/new flooring allowance) OR Pay your HOA Dues for a YEAR! Welcome to Sunny Florida and Del Webb Southshore Falls... a Very Active 55+ Gated Community! You will love this Beautiful Meticulously Maintained 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, Plus Den, Luxury Villa with a Private Screened Lanai and 2 car garage... Year around or as your vacation retreat! From the moment you arrive, you get a peaceful feeling approaching the front porch where you can sit and gaze across to the pond and watch the morning activities of many bird species while sipping your coffee as the sun rises.  As you enter your Villa you will know you have found the perfect place to call home! Many upgrades feature rounded wall corners for a smooth contour look, additional front glass/screen door for a cross breeze from the lanai through your home, Ceiling fans throughout, and French doors to your Office/Den. Spacious chef's Kitchen has a closet pantry, tall wood cabinets, an Eat-In area Plus a Breakfast Bar and Includes All Appliances; Refrigerator, Dishwasher, Microwave, NEW Stove, and Disposal! NEW A/C in 2018 You will love the spacious floorplan that accommodates a dining room table and large living area that leads out through sliding doors to your private lanai overlooking a huge greenbelt of green lush landscape. Step out of your screened Lanai to sit and enjoy your own intimate garden area. The Best part is. your lawn maintenance, exterior painting, and tile roof cleaning is all included! Spacious owner's suite has a large walk-in closet & en-suite bathroom and your guests will love their bedroom with guest bathroom steps away. The Inside Laundry room includes a Washer and Dryer! The 2 car Garage with auto opener has a utility sink and a Rollout Screen Door entry directly to kitchen!  Enjoy Resort Living in this 55+ 24 24-hour Guard Gated Community...the Best Kept Secret Beyond Compare. Pets Welcome! Very low HOAs (no cdd's) include your lawn & landscape maintenance, exterior painting, recreation area in a vacation-style setting with Lagoon Heated Pool, Resistance pool, Spa, Fitness center, tennis, bocce & pickle-ball, walking trails, bike club, golf putting greens, arts & crafts, billiards, Internet Café & so many Fun Activities & Entertainment. Close drive to World Renowned Sugar Sand Beaches, the Gulf of Mexico & Tampa Bay International Airport. Come get away from it all at Del Webb SouthShore Falls and Live, Laugh & Love Life!
